{"tid":1955754,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌哂你哋老母","createTime":"2020-04-02T16:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T17:56:15.000Z","uid":266467,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69c0a188ff2693693a1e9ee2f4a600c3a8c3567c","tid":1955754,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌哂你哋老母！</span></span></span><br />\n係咪光復咗香港 五大訴求達到左啦？ 做咩成個熱門都係食玩膠同睇女post？<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登已死</span></span></span></span> 連我個<span style=\"color: blue;\">淺藍老母</span>都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既？<br />\n<br />\n應承我 唔好當手足係condom 我哋要揸住佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 千祈唔可以中五毛分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n煲底見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"6c4cfd69b0c894d6a907042704f3dfa92e40dfbb","tid":1955754,"uid":206987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4276323c63edeaa5bea10e20dac1c1411f2e4ac","tid":1955754,"uid":41290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d22aa6ee621130e60cbb3ddd8f4549ad05a7ccab","tid":1955754,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cl